QuestData.Title: Neferset Prison
QuestData.Description: Hieroglyphs depicting a chained Tol'vir mark the southeastern corner of the map.$B$BPerhaps Tahet was brought there when he was imprisoned.
QuestData.LogDescription: Go to the Neferset Prison Camp and find the whereabouts of Tahet.
QuestData.RewardText: If the prisoner's information is true, Tahet is in great danger.
